*Entering through a brown door in [[Level 877]] leads one here;
*Entering any door in The Watching Basement of [[Level 293]] leads one here;
*Noclipping through any depiction of "The Red Scare" in [[Level 560]] leads one here;
*Noclipping through a cartridge of the classic Tetris video game in [[Level 40]] sends one here;
*Entering a door with Russian signage on [[Level 17]] leads one here;
*Getting arrested after mentioning damning topics to PAPs in [[Level 912]] leads one here.
----
*Rarely, some who have slept ended up in another level of the Backrooms;
*Jumping down a bottomless sinkhole sends one to [[Level 6]];
*Noclipping through snow sends one to [[Level 65]];
*Rarely, rusted doors in the buildings might lead one to [[Level 521]];
*Noclipping in a drug store sends one to [[Level 570]];
*Entering through a black door in a dilapidated hallway sends one to [[Level 412]];
*Any noclipping within a khrushchevka sends one to [[Level 238]];
*Certain buildings within secluded locations will take one to [[Level 340]].
